title: Anabolic Rough Sex 2 (DVD) [complete] dir. Khan Tusion
description:
ANABOLIC ROUGH SEX 2
DIR. KHAN TUSION

Anabolic took this film out of print shortly after its release (along with Part 1).  Neither was ever issued on DVD.  VHS rips float around the net for both but only in pieces.  Once upon a time they were converted to VCDs but one of them is VERY hard to come by -- I had to stoop to using eMule to download the other which took about 10 days with the client running 24 hours a day.

I then took the video files and authored a DVD using Sony DVD Architect.  The sequence is correct and all footage is intact as I know it.

ENJOY -- COMMENT -- SEED
